* Libraries from Files
** Workspace files
***_ 500 MB file size limit
***_ Path: /Workspace/Users/.../mylib.whl
***_ Import via workspace Import dialog
** Unity Catalog volumes
***_ Enhanced governance
***_ Access control via UC permissions
***_ READ VOLUME permission required
***_ Path: /Volumes/main/eng/libs/mylib.whl
** requirements.txt support
***_ Databricks Runtime 15.0+
***_ Multiple packages in one file
***_ Works with workspace files & volumes
** Standard access mode
***_ Paths must be in allowlist
***_ Applies to workspace files & volumes
@endmindmap
